Workhouse (Work Management System)
Nico Nebel
26.06.2026


// XA
NOTE READ USERNAME
GRAB 300
COPY F X
DROP

NOTE READ FILE 199
LINK 800
GRAB 199
MARK READ_199FILE
  TEST F = X
  FJMP READ_199FILE
COPY F X
COPY F X
DROP

NOTE MANIPUL USERFILE
LINK 799
GRAB X

NOTE CALC SUM
SEEK 2
COPY 0 X

MARK READ_USERFILE
  ADDI X F X
  TEST EOF
  FJMP READ_USERFILE

NOTE OVERWRITE 75
SEEK -9999
SEEK 2

MARK WRITE_USERFILE
  COPY 75 F
  SUBI X 75 X
  TEST X > 74
  TJMP WRITE_USERFILE
COPY X F
HALT